Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.49,0:24:33.66,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,Next Conan's hint!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.66,0:24:34.99,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,A shelf!
